{#- One-line, secret-free summary of an AWS profile: region, named profile,
    role ARN, whitelisted plugin fields, and the credential mode. Secret fields
    (secret_access_key, session_token) are stripped by datus before rendering;
    access_key_id is checked for presence only and never emitted. -#}
{%- macro aws_summary(cfg, extra_fields=[]) -%}
{%- set parts = [] -%}
{%- if cfg.get("region") %}{% set _ = parts.append("region=" ~ cfg.get("region")) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if cfg.get("profile") %}{% set _ = parts.append("aws_profile=" ~ cfg.get("profile")) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if cfg.get("role_arn") %}{% set _ = parts.append("role=" ~ cfg.get("role_arn")) %}{% endif -%}
{%- for field in extra_fields -%}
{%- if cfg.get(field) %}{% set _ = parts.append(field ~ "=" ~ cfg.get(field)) %}{% endif -%}
{%- endfor -%}
{%- if cfg.get("access_key_id") %}{% set _ = parts.append("creds=keys") -%}
{%- elif cfg.get("role_arn") %}{% set _ = parts.append("creds=assume-role") -%}
{%- else %}{% set _ = parts.append("creds=chain") %}{% endif -%}
{{- parts | join(", ") -}}
{%- endmacro -%}
{% if profiles %}
## QuickSight
Manage Amazon QuickSight through `datus quicksight <group> <subcommand>` (`--profile <env>` before the group).
Groups: `datasets`, `datasources`, `dashboards`, `analyses`, `templates`, `themes`, `folders` (list/describe + create/update/delete), `users`/`groups`/`namespaces` (identity admin), `refresh` (SPICE ingestions: run [--wait]/status/list/cancel + schedules), `account` (settings, subscription), `assets` (asset-bundle export/import). `dashboards embed-url[-anonymous]` mints viewing links. Reads run freely; mutations (create/update/delete/publish/permissions/membership/import) always confirm; `refresh run/cancel` are routine. Requires `aws_account_id`; user/group/namespace ops use `identity_region`. Add `-o json` for machine-readable output. Consult the `quicksight` skill before non-trivial commands.
Environments ({{ profiles | length }}):
{% for name, cfg in profiles.items() -%}
- {{ name }}: {{ aws_summary(cfg, ["aws_account_id"]) }}
{% endfor -%}
{% else %}
## QuickSight (installed, not configured)
The `datus quicksight` CLI is installed but has no environment configured.
Run the `quicksight-setup` skill to configure one.
{% endif %}
